1
00:00:19,580 --> 00:00:21,980
What's hidden in this room?

2
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:24,660
He never lets me near it usually.

3
00:00:38,580 --> 00:00:39,140
This...

4
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:40,060
This...

5
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,660
This is his master?

6
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:44,460
I really

7
00:00:45,060 --> 00:00:47,340
do look exactly like her.

8
00:01:10,660 --> 00:01:11,260
Yaoyang.

9
00:01:20,100 --> 00:01:20,620
What...

10
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:22,340
What just happened?

11
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:30,360
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 16]

12
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:47,420
I can't find the Shadow Moon Pendant.

13
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:49,180
The fiendish aura of Xieyun

14
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,900
will soon be detected
by the immortal sects.

15
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:52,940
I need to think of another way

16
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:54,260
to suppress the fiendish aura.

17
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,120
[Soul-Mixing Pill]
The Soul-Mixing Pill

18
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,140
can suppress the fiendish aura.

19
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:22,220
Refining it requires

20
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:25,060
nurturing the Soul-Mixing Herb

21
00:02:26,220 --> 00:02:27,060
with the power of one's spirit.

22
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:55,140
What are you three standing here for?

23
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:56,820
Come taste my cooking.

24
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,500
- No, thanks.
- No, thanks.

25
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:17,460
I'm not here for your ingredients.

26
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:18,820
I just came to tell you

27
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:20,340
not to make dinner for me tonight.

28
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:22,300
You're not eating?

29
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,540
I don't have an appetite today.

30
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:34,900
I won't eat.

31
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,380
What?

32
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:38,740
You're not eating either?

33
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:42,100
What's going on?

34
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,460
None of them are eating?

35
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:46,580
Yaoyang.

36
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:47,540
Yuxun.

37
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,460
I've started fasting
for cultivation recently.

38
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:50,700
I won't eat.

39
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:52,060
Just so you know,

40
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:52,860
you don't need to

41
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:54,700
make food for me for the next few days.

42
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:55,860
Alright.

43
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:02,740
Something must have happened last night.

44
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:05,300
I missed all the fun.

45
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:24,140
Why do you have the curtain drawn

46
00:04:24,140 --> 00:04:25,140
in broad daylight?

47
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,060
I...

48
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,460
I'm copying the mantra.

49
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:28,900
Can you leave?

50
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:30,540
Alright.

51
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:32,500
It's hard for a girl to bring it up.

52
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:35,180
I'd better go ask Little Fox.

53
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:46,260
Did you have a fight?

54
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:48,660
No.

55
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:52,260
Then why is the vibe so strange?

56
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:57,940
You still haven't answered me.

57
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,820
At this rate,

58
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,340
when will they ever fall in love?

59
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:08,340
Wan'er is waiting for me.

60
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:11,460
No way.

61
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,620
Looks like I'll have to step in.

62
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:16,260
Little Fox,

63
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:17,860
I already know.

64
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:20,420
There's something up
with the three of you.

65
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:22,500
How do you know?

66
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:24,660
I'm a one-of-a-kind mushroom

67
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:26,260
from ancient times.

68
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:28,500
A little calculation
and I know everything.

69
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:30,780
Forget it.

70
00:05:30,780 --> 00:05:31,500
I can't think of anything else.

71
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,060
Anyway,

72
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,100
I can see right

73
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:35,820
through your little situation.

74
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:42,180
I think love between a man and woman

75
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,500
should be mutual.

76
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:46,860
You can't force it.

77
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:48,740
Did Miss Ruoxi

78
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:49,740
reject you?

79
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,460
She didn't say it outright,

80
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,420
but I can feel that she...

81
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:58,980
She's a girl!

82
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,580
What matters most to a girl?

83
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:01,940
Reserve.

84
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:03,260
How could a girl

85
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,820
just say she likes you out loud?

86
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:07,500
If the one she loves isn't me,

87
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:10,860
I can't save her.

88
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,700
When did Miss Ruoxi

89
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:14,340
reject you?

90
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:15,740
I think

91
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:16,940
she likes you.

92
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:18,140
Really?

93
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:20,500
After I gave her that book

94
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,540
"Neither Red nor Green",

95
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:23,020
wasn't she pretty eager
to learn from you?

96
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,860
How can you miss

97
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,380
such an obvious hint?

98
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:31,100
What hint?

99
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,740
What does making her love me

100
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:36,780
have to do with that book?

101
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,460
Do I really have to spell it out?

102
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:40,980
It's...

103
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:42,220
You two have to...

104
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:42,780
You know,

105
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:44,140
that.

106
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:45,660
That.

107
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,060
You still don't get it?

108
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,460
Let me be straight with you.

109
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:57,940
Ruoxi was formed

110
00:06:57,940 --> 00:07:00,340
from a wisp of Bai Xiyin's remnant soul.

111
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,060
She was born with an incomplete nature.

112
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:03,580
Only through dual cultivation

113
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:04,820
with the one she loves

114
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,660
can she become whole

115
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:08,020
and restore her soul.

116
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:09,780
What did you say?

117
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:10,500
Dual cultivation...?

118
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:18,020
Why are you only telling me this now?

119
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,740
How was I supposed to know
you'd be so clueless?

120
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:22,660
Usually, when two people are in love,

121
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:24,740
that kind of thing
just happens naturally.

122
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:27,140
But

123
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:30,020
I think her heart belongs to Yaoyang,

124
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:30,980
not me.

125
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,180
He's not an option.

126
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:34,180
Why not?

127
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:35,540
I said he's not an option,
and that's it.

128
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:37,220
Anyway, you need to act fast.

129
00:07:37,660 --> 00:07:38,260
Otherwise,

130
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:41,660
Miss Ruoxi's life might be in danger.

131
00:07:43,580 --> 00:07:45,340
How much time do I have?

132
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:49,220
Less than a month.

133
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:53,460
But dual...

134
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:56,820
That kind of thing

135
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,940
requires mutual consent even more.

136
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,580
How could it be forced?

137
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:04,380
Miss Ruoxi was born
with an incomplete nature.

138
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,380
How could she understand romantic love?

139
00:08:06,980 --> 00:08:07,580
You need to

140
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:08,820
take the lead on this.

141
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,580
You should really read that book

142
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:12,140
"Neither Red nor Green".

143
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,460
I'll lend you a hand

144
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:14,980
when it counts.

145
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:01,300
I made you this soup with the finest

146
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:02,980
worry-dispelling herbs.

147
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:04,980
How can you drink it now?

148
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:06,180
I don't have

149
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:07,940
an appetite anyway.

150
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:11,940
This soup is meant to ease your worries.

151
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:13,100
I

152
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:14,180
have no worries!

153
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:17,060
Your worries

154
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:18,580
are written all over your face.

155
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:21,820
Is it because of that man?

156
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,100
Has he been

157
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:26,740
cold to you lately,

158
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,180
and you're

159
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:30,140
feeling a bit resentful?

160
00:09:33,060 --> 00:09:34,180
I knew it!

161
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:35,780
That's not it at all!

162
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:38,700
Maybe he's been distant

163
00:09:39,180 --> 00:09:40,420
for his own reasons.

164
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:41,500
This is exactly when

165
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,020
you shouldn't give up.

166
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:45,220
If you two miss your chance now,

167
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,740
you might regret it
for the rest of your life.

168
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:50,940
So serious?

169
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:52,220
Of course.

170
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:54,820
I had a friend.

171
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:57,460
She fell deeply in love with a man.

172
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,180
But because of some misunderstandings,

173
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:01,380
they ended up apart.

174
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,020
In the end,

175
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:05,580
they were separated forever.

176
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,380
So hard.

177
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:09,380
I can't think of anything else.

178
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,460
So,

179
00:10:13,260 --> 00:10:14,460
maybe

180
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:16,260
I've been too harsh on Yaoyang?

181
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,180
What if

182
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:22,260
the person he likes

183
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:24,220
is someone similar to me,

184
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:25,740
but not me?

185
00:10:26,580 --> 00:10:27,380
What then?

186
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,340
Everyone has a past.

187
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:34,180
You can't cling to the past forever.

188
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:36,140
That only hurts each other.

189
00:10:37,060 --> 00:10:37,820
If you go on like this,

190
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:39,260
you'll end up like my friend,

191
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:40,980
filled with lifelong regret.

192
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:44,780
Actually,

193
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:46,940
come to think of it,

194
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:49,740
he's usually

195
00:10:50,060 --> 00:10:51,580
quite good to me.

196
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:54,260
Maybe

197
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:56,020
I really am being

198
00:10:56,780 --> 00:10:57,980
too stubborn?

199
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:01,860
Romantic love

200
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:03,180
is an art.

201
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:04,700
It's just that you haven't learned

202
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:06,180
the skills of courtship yet.

203
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,780
So you've gone astray.

204
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:09,220
What skills?

205
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:12,980
Don't tell me you haven't read

206
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:15,020
that book I gave you.

207
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:17,020
Every time

208
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:18,740
I show that book

209
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,460
to Tu Jing,

210
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:23,140
his face turns bright red.

211
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,620
He even avoids me.

212
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:25,620
So...

213
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,380
I could tell right away

214
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,780
it wasn't going anywhere.

215
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:31,260
Listen,

216
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:32,460
some men

217
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:33,780
like women to be forward,

218
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,260
while others

219
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,420
prefer them reserved.

220
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:38,820
Men can change.

221
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:39,540
Today

222
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:40,980
you might like this type,

223
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:41,780
tomorrow

224
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:43,660
you might be drawn to another.

225
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:45,180
So

226
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:46,980
you really need to be observant.

227
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:47,860
That's the way

228
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:50,020
to capture a man's heart.

229
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:52,140
Sounds

230
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:54,020
complicated.

231
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:56,340
Put simply,

232
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,820
do the opposite.

233
00:11:58,420 --> 00:11:59,940
When he says "no",

234
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,540
it means "yes".

235
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:03,260
When he says "yes",

236
00:12:03,260 --> 00:12:03,620
well,

237
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:05,140
it still means "yes".

238
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:05,980
Do you get it?

239
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:07,980
So

240
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,340
which is it,

241
00:12:10,740 --> 00:12:12,380
"no" or "yes"?

242
00:12:13,020 --> 00:12:14,460
Little Fox, a grown man,

243
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,820
can't swallow his pride.

244
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:18,300
I guess I'll have to let Miss Ruoxi
take the lead.

245
00:12:20,380 --> 00:12:21,100
Alright,

246
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:22,380
come with me to a place.

247
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:23,660
Once we get there,

248
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:24,980
you'll know what to do.

249
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:26,700
What place?

250
00:12:26,940 --> 00:12:27,820
You'll know when we get there.

251
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,460
But I'm telling you,

252
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:31,660
this stays between us.

253
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:32,900
You absolutely can't tell those two.

254
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:36,780
Okay.

255
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:37,620
Let's make a pinky swear.

256
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:39,660
Pinky swear.

257
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:40,700
I promise I won't tell anyone.

258
00:12:41,950 --> 00:12:44,460
[Yingchun Pavilion]

259
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:44,940
We're here.

260
00:12:47,340 --> 00:12:48,220
Sir,

261
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:49,420
is this your first time here?

262
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:50,220
Let's go.

263
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,100
Come on, Xiaotaohong.

264
00:12:52,060 --> 00:12:52,900
Sir, please come in.

265
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:57,580
Sir.

266
00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,980
I'll wait for you upstairs.

267
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:12,580
What is this place?

268
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:15,380
These women

269
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,180
are masters of romance.

270
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:19,380
They excel at capturing a man's heart.

271
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:20,300
You'll need to

272
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,700
pay close attention and learn.

273
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:34,380
I

274
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:36,140
think I'll just head back.

275
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:38,180
You're already here.

276
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,780
You need to learn a trick or two
before you go.

277
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:40,580
Let's go.

278
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:41,580
Come on.

279
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,380
Ruhua.

280
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:47,500
I'm leaving this to you.

281
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:49,220
Sure. No problem.

282
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:50,780
Pay close attention.

283
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,140
I'll come check on you later.

284
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,420
Where are you going?

285
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,780
Xiaotaohong, here I come!

286
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:56,740
Where are you going?

287
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:58,780
Come on.

288
00:13:59,140 --> 00:14:00,180
Learn from me.

289
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:02,620
First,

290
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,580
your gaze at a man

291
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:05,780
has to be captivating.

292
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:09,740
Start

293
00:14:10,180 --> 00:14:12,780
by looking him straight in the eyes.

294
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,380
Then lower your head.

295
00:14:19,980 --> 00:14:21,940
Put on a shy expression.

296
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:30,860
Men love this look the most.

